className="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-neutral-lightGray dark:border-neutral-darkGray rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-neutral-charcoal text-text-light-primary dark:text-text-dark-primary ..."
```
**Problem:** `neutral-lightGray`, `neutral-darkGray`, and `neutral-charcoal` are NOT semantic color tokens

**Lines 786-799 (Action buttons):**
```tsx
